Package: Norimon
Title: Utility Functions for the National Insect Monitoring in Norway
Version: 0.0.0.9011
Authors@R: 
    person("Jens", "Åström", , "jens.astrom@nina.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6114-0440"))
Description: This package provides functions to read and analyse data connected with the national monitoring scheme of insects in Norway
  It documentents the methods used in the analysis of the data, and in the calculation of indicators that describe the ecological state of the insect communities.
  In addition, it provides outside users with access to the data for replicating the analyses and further exploration. 
